quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Mana Abarumwa olwa boola khubandu ba Luti
  15,62,(Luti) naboola; “Toto enywe muli Abandu balamanyishe tawe.”
  15,63,Nibaboola mbu; “mana efwe khukhureerere kalia kabakholelanga obukanakani” nomulembe
  15,64,"“Ne khukhwitsile khubulaamba, netoto efwe khuboolanga obwatoto.”"
  15,65,"“Kho rula nende Abandu bawo, ebise bilala mubise bieshilo, nawe abalondekhwo, neyesiyesi mwinywe alakalukhanakhwo okhuhenga inyuma tawe, nemutsie wamulomesibungwa"
  15,66,"Nenikhumubusilia likhuwa elo, mbu emisi chiabu chitsa okhutetwa mumabwibwi"
  15,67,Ne Abandu belitokho elo nibetsa nibasangalile
  15,68,(Lut) Naboola mbu; “Toto bano ni abacheni banje khomulafimbia omurwe tawe”
  15,69,"“Ne murie Nyasaye, ne mulafimbia omurwe tawe”"
  15,70,"Nibaboola mbu: “efwe shikhwakhukaniakho (okhurera) Abandu (belwanyi)"
  15,71,"Naboola mbu: “ bano nabakhana banje itse ebahelesie(mubateshie) toto enywe nimuli abakholanga"
  15,72,"Nditsuba khulubaka lulwo, mbu : “abo bali mubumesi bwabu nibanyakhananga eshikhaya.”"
  15,73,Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi
  15,74,"Mana nikhukhola hasi wabu okhuba hekulu, mana nikhubakwisilia ifula ya machina yeliloba lwomumulilo.”"
  15,75,Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubandu baretsanga amakhuwa khushichelo
  15,76,Ne toto tsingongo etso tsili khutsinjila tsiburungwakhwo
  15,77,Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubasuubili
  15,78,Netoto Abandu bomushitsimi bali ababii
  15,79,"Mana nikhubahelesia eshinyasio, ne ebialo bibili bino bili khunjila ili habulafu"